415
00:41:04,790 --> 00:41:07,560
Do you know why?

416
00:41:09,980 --> 00:41:11,920
For peace and stability.

417
00:41:13,020 --> 00:41:15,050
You understand now?

418
00:41:19,990 --> 00:41:21,960
I understand.

419
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:24,730
My poor child...

420
00:41:26,160 --> 00:41:28,980
Do not hate the crown prince anymore.

421
00:41:29,590 --> 00:41:35,610
If you are going to hate, hate the emperor of Li Empire.

422
00:41:36,290 --> 00:41:40,880
He is the one who ordered the crown prince to launch an attack on Danchi.

423
00:41:41,770 --> 00:41:46,750
If Xi State and Danchi want to reprimand anyone,

424
00:41:47,820 --> 00:41:51,540
