425
00:41:52,960 --> 00:41:56,130
- Great-Grandmother...
- Because...

426
00:41:56,130 --> 00:42:00,800
I am the emperor's grandmother.

427
00:42:00,800 --> 00:42:03,880
I am the crown prince's great-grandmother.

428
00:42:03,880 --> 00:42:09,840
The Grand Empress Dowager of Li Empire.

